beer.beer_description:
Come visit the local Milk Bar. Grab yourself a Rainbow Ice Cream Cone. It’s a smoothie style sour brewed using our Sour Smoothie Base then loaded with a stupid amount of Strawberries, banana, cherry puree, blueberries, milk sugar, bubblegum and vanilla softserve icecream. Enjoy the Sundae!
